label: AB11_tI48_141_b_aci-001
title: BaCd$_{11}$ Structure
comments:
(Sanderson, 1953) gave the atomic positions in setting 1 of space group $I4_{1}/amd$ \#141.  We used FINDSYM to transform this to the standard setting 2. 
 The ICSD entry is for SrCd$_{11}$, as BaCd$_{11}$ is not in the ICSD database, despite being the lead structure in (Sanderson, 1953). The lattice constants of the two structures are very similar, and the atomic positions are identical.
